# Build context hygiene for the Railway Dockerfiles (backend/ + app/).
# Keep: every workspace's src + package.json, yarn.lock, .yarnrc.yml, prisma/.
# Drop: installed deps (fresh install), build output, secrets, the Hardhat tree.

# deps — reinstalled in the image
**/node_modules
.yarn/cache
.yarn/install-state.gz

# build output — rebuilt in the image
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# secrets — NEVER bake into an image (Railway injects env at runtime)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# the Hardhat / contracts tree is not a workspace and not needed to build backend or app
blockchain

# vcs / editor / docs / claude
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
docs
**/*.md
.claude
app/dist
backend/dist
